{"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/9Ensembles15CloudFileSystemP","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A cloud file system backed by Box, using the Box Swift SDK ("},{"code":"BoxSdkGen","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/ensemblesbox\/boxcloudfilesystem"]}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/init(client:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/client","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/isConnected"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/connect()","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/contentsOfDirectory(atPath:)","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/createDirectory(atPath:)","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/downloadFile(atPath:toLocalFile:)","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/fetchUserIdentity()","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/fileExists(atPath:)","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/removeItem(atPath:)","doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox\/BoxCloudFileSystem\/uploadLocalFile(atPath:toPath:)"],"title":"Instance Methods"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BoxCloudFileSystem","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:12EnsemblesBox0B15CloudFileSystemC","role":"symbol","title":"BoxCloudFileSystem","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"BoxCloudFileSystem","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"EnsemblesBox"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/EnsemblesBox\/documentation\/EnsemblesBox"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BoxCloudFileSystem","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This backend requires the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/box\/box-ios-sdk.git","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"package. With the source distribution, enable the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Box"},{"type":"text","text":" package trait and SPM resolves it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"automatically. With the binary distribution (XCFrameworks), add BoxSDK as a separate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"package dependency in your project."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Important","style":"important"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Box uses numeric IDs rather than paths to identify files and folders. This backend"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"bridges the path-based "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CloudFileSystem"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol onto Box’s ID-based API by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"walking the folder hierarchy to resolve Ensembles paths"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(e.g. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ensembleId\/events\/file.json"},{"type":"text","text":") to Box folder and file IDs."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Resolved IDs are cached in internal dictionaries to minimize API calls. The cache"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is invalidated when items are deleted or when not-found errors indicate stale entries."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The app creates and configures a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BoxClient"},{"type":"text","text":" with its own authentication"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and injects it at init time:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let auth = BoxDeveloperTokenAuth(token: \"your-token\")","let client = BoxClient(auth: auth)","let cloudFS = BoxCloudFileSystem(client: client)"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Authentication","anchor":"Authentication"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Box Swift SDK supports multiple authentication methods. Create a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BoxClient"},{"type":"text","text":" with the appropriate auth for your use case:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Developer Token (testing only)","anchor":"Developer-Token-testing-only"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Get a short-lived token from "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.box.com\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"under your app’s configuration page. These tokens expire after 60 minutes."}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let auth = BoxDeveloperTokenAuth(token: \"your-developer-token\")","let client = BoxClient(auth: auth)","let cloudFS = BoxCloudFileSystem(client: client)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"OAuth-20-production-apps","type":"heading","text":"OAuth 2.0 (production apps)","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register your app at "},{"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"developer.box.com","type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.box.com\/","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"developer.box.com"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"configure an OAuth 2.0 redirect URI:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let config = OAuthConfig(clientId: \"your-client-id\", clientSecret: \"your-secret\")","let auth = BoxOAuth(config: config)","\/\/ Call auth.authorize(url:) with your redirect URL after the OAuth flow","let client = BoxClient(auth: auth)","let cloudFS = BoxCloudFileSystem(client: client)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Client-Credentials-Grant-server-side","level":3,"text":"Client Credentials Grant (server-side)","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For server-to-server integration without user interaction:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let config = CCGConfig(","    clientId: \"your-client-id\",","    clientSecret: \"your-secret\",","    userId: \"user-id\"",")","let auth = BoxCCGAuth(config: config)","let client = BoxClient(auth: auth)","let cloudFS = BoxCloudFileSystem(client: client)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Threading","level":2,"text":"Threading","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This class is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@unchecked Sendable"},{"type":"text","text":". The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BoxClient"},{"type":"text","text":" handles its own thread"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"safety internally. Mutable state (caches, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"loggedIn"},{"type":"text","text":" flag) is accessed only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from async methods that are serialized by the ensemble’s operation queue."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://EnsemblesBox/documentation/EnsemblesBox/BoxCloudF